-- Toshiba, Samsung Sign Preliminary Agreement to Outsource Chip Production
-- B y   J u n   Y a n g
-- 2010-12-24T06:47:11Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-24/toshiba-samsung-sign-preliminary-agreement-to-outsource-chip-production.html
Toshiba Corp. said it signed an
initial agreement with Samsung Electronics Co. regarding the
outsourcing of production of system chips.  Toshiba is also in talks with other companies, Hiroki
Yamazaki, a Toshiba spokesman, said by phone today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
